{
  "stem": "27507.10",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was-- I mean, the poorer Jews were financed by the richer Jews in that case.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But Kopers didn't have much out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they had a lot of trouble, because they had, after all, to keep them somehow nourished.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They had-- Marta had to go, and to buy food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And every time there was-- and there were other people living in this-- just behind the wall.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were-- and any louder word could-- could finish with all of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "If neighbors were suspicious, it would be enough, a word from a neighbor, to bury all of us on the spot, practically.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The neighbors never-- they were never found out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The neighbors made jokes about Marta carrying big baskets of food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But they never, somehow, found out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They made jokes about the fact that the windows were always covered with curtains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But, somehow, they didn't suspect completely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And those Jews who were in-- although they should have been behaving 100%, they didn't behave so well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Sometimes they-- we had scenes sometimes, and people-- the nerves were on edge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And people were sometimes shouting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And people were not always behaving as well as they should have behaved in a condition of complete hide.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But we must have been extra-- something, somehow, there was a luck that was difficult to-- to explain.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So there were about-- why Koper started it, as I said, there was probably material reasons for that to start.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But later, it turned into something different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And then-- so we were altogether about 10 or 11 people there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There was my Aunt Hania, with her friend, a woman called Berta.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
